9 An Act relating to officers; amending 51 O.S. 2021,
Section 152, as last amended by Section 1, Chapter
10 314, O.S.L. 2025 (51 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 152),
which relates to The Governmental Tort Claims Act;
11 modifying definition; and providing an effective
